sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant R as Route
    participant Ctrl as CategoriesController
    participant M as Category Model
    participant Q as Query Builder
    participant Res as CategoryResource

    C->>R: GET /api/categories
    R->>Ctrl: __invoke()
    
    Ctrl->>M: Category::query()
    M-->>Ctrl: Query Builder instance
    
    Ctrl->>Q: where('is_active', true)
    Q-->>Ctrl: Query Builder (filtered)
    
    Ctrl->>Q: with('children')
    Q-->>Ctrl: Query Builder (with eager loading)
    
    Ctrl->>Q: orderBy('name')
    Ctrl->>Q: get()
    
    Q->>M: execute query
    M-->>Q: Collection of Category models
    
    Note over Ctrl: Each Category has children loaded
    
    loop for each Category
        Ctrl->>Res: toArray()
        Res-->>Ctrl: transformed array with children
    end
    
    Ctrl-->>C: JSON response with categories and nested children
